# Server-side only — used exclusively by api/analyze.ts (a Vercel serverless
# function). Never prefix this with VITE_, or it would be bundled into the
# client-side JS and exposed to anyone who opens DevTools.
#
# Get a free key at https://console.groq.com
GROQ_API_KEY=

# Set this in your Vercel project's Environment Variables dashboard for
# production/preview deployments — this .env file is for local reference
# only and is not read by `vite dev` (which has no serverless function
# runtime). To test the real AI call locally, use `vercel dev` instead.
